OL,3,C'Like Coming Home': Russell T. Davies
OL,4,Creturns to Manchester for new drama
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports Entertainment
OL,7,FCorrespondent was on the red carpet
OL,8,Fand spoke to Russel T. Davies
OL,10,FCritically acclaimed TV producer
OL,11,FRussell T. Davies has said returning
OL,12,Fto Manchester to film his latest drama
OL,13,Ffelt "like coming home" - nearly three
OL,14,Fdecades after his groundbreaking hit
OL,15,FQueer as Folk.
OL,17,FThe Welsh screenwriter, also known for
OL,18,FDoctor Who and It's A Sin, was among
OL,19,Fthe stars in attendance at a launch
OL,20,Fevent at HOME Cinema for his new
OL,21,Fseries Tip Toe on 28 May.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
