OL,3,C'Like Coming Home': Russell T. Davies
OL,4,Creturns to Manchester for new drama
OL,6,FThe five-part series follows the
OL,7,Fescalating conflict between two men
OL,8,Fwho have been neighbours for 15 years:
OL,9,FLeo Struthers, who owns a bar on Canal
OL,10,FStreet and Clive Goss, a struggling
OL,11,Felectrician.
OL,13,F"It's a Manchester show made by a
OL,14,FManchester company, with a lot of
OL,15,FNorth West talent, this is a big
OL,16,Fnight," Russell said speaking on the
OL,17,Fred carpet.
OL,19,F"I love working in Manchester, I've
OL,20,Fbeen here almost 40 years, I adore it."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780229466
OL,3,C'Like Coming Home': Russell T. Davies
OL,4,Creturns to Manchester for new drama
OL,6,FThe peace between them shatters when
OL,7,FLeo hires Clive to do some work at his
OL,8,Fbar, but the job triggers the
OL,9,Fworkman's deep-seated, underlying
OL,10,Fhomophobia and transphobia.
OL,12,FThe series stems from Russell T.
OL,13,FDavies' view that the increasingly
OL,14,Ftoxic online discourse surrounding
OL,15,FLGBTQ+ people has forced the queer
OL,16,Fcommunity to walk on eggshells just to
OL,17,Favoid being noticed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
