PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780229466
OL,3,C'Like Coming Home': Russell T. Davies
OL,4,Creturns to Manchester for new drama
OL,6,FStarring Alan Cumming as Leo and David
OL,7,FMorrissey as Clive, the series
OL,8,Flaunches 27 years after Davies'
OL,9,FManchester-set Queer as Folk, one of
OL,10,Fthe most important queer TV dramas of
OL,11,Fall time.
OL,13,F"I love it here - it's my proper home.
OL,14,FI adore it. I adore the people, I
OL,15,Fadore the crew and the hard work. I
OL,16,Flove the spirit up here!" Russell said.
OL,18,F"You couldn't ask for two better
OL,19,Factors. They're best friends in real
OL,20,Flife and have never appeared together
OL,21,Fon screen."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
