PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780229466
OL,3,C'Like Coming Home': Russell T. Davies
OL,4,Creturns to Manchester for new drama
OL,6,FDavid Morrissey, from Liverpool, said:
OL,7,F"What's really inspiring for me about
OL,8,Fthe North West is how much film and
OL,9,Ftelevision is made there, and how much
OL,10,Ftheatre is there as well."
OL,12,FAs part of Channel 4's campaign to
OL,13,Fpromote the show, oversized, and
OL,14,Fhighly insulting post-it notes have
OL,15,Fappeared on the sides of two ordinary
OL,16,Fhouse in Salford.
OL,18,FStanding at a massive five metres
OL,19,Ftall, these giant notes are designed
OL,20,Fto look like a real-life neighbourhood
OL,21,Ffeud spiralling out of control,
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
